"title": "6195: impenitence, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6195",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The seriousness of the failure to repent is frequently underlined in Scripture, which provides numerous examples of impenitence and its consequences.</p>\n<h2>Warnings against impenitence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:25\">HEB 12:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:6-2Chr30:9\">2CH 30:6–30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:1\">JER 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:9-Jer18:10\">JER 18:9–18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:6\">EZK 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:2\">HOS 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:7\">MAL 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:1-Luke13:5\">LUK 13:1–13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:19\">HEB 3:7–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:8\">PSA 95:7–95:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">REV 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:16\">REV 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>Results of impenitence</h2>\n<h3>Storing up wrath for the day of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20\">2CH 24:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:16-2Chr36:17\">2CH 36:16–36:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:12\">JOB 36:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:24-Prov1:26\">PRO 1:24–1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:9\">AMO 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:21\">2PE 2:21</a></p>\n<h3>Condemnation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:20\">MAT 11:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Hardness of heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:13-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:13–13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:11\">HEB 3:7–3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual blindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:40\">JHN 12:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:8\">ROM 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Being forsaken by God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:20\">2KI 17:13–17:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:6-2Chr29:9\">2CH 29:6–29:9</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of impenitence</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:15\">EXO 8:15</a> <em>Pharaoh</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:19\">JDG 2:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:19\">1SA 8:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:26-Neh9:29\">NEH 9:26–9:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:13-Dan9:14\">DAN 9:13–9:14</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:23\">2CH 33:23</a> <em>Amon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:13\">2CH 36:13</a> <em>Zedekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:15\">JER 6:15</a> <em>inhabitants of Jerusalem</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:31\">MAT 21:31</a> <em>the elders and chief priests</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18\">LUK 18:18</a> <em>the hard-hearted</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:18–1:23</a> <em>the pagans</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:21-Rev2:27\">REV 2:21–2:27</a> <em>Jezebel, the false prophetess</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">REV 9:20–9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:8-Rev16:11\">REV 16:8–16:11</a></p>",
